  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 08a31708ff494388b94a36253e9e9a5c, type: 3}
  m_Name: DemonData_Beelzebabe
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: LSG::LSG.DemonData_Beelzebabe
  demonName: Beelzebabe
  canDateDemonMultipleTimes: 1
  introDialogue: 'Jackpot, baby!  She''s all the lover you could want, all the partner
    you''ve dreamt about: vivacious, bodacious, and up for anything.  Her horns are
    shiny, her eyes pierce your soul, and she''s got a knowing confidence that sends
    a shiver through your entire being.


    "Well now, been a while since someone
    knew enough to call on me..." she says, with a voice like liquid sex, "but can
    you take me all the way?"'
  minimumPowerLevel: 20
  maximumPowerLevel: 99
  outcome: Her smile sends shockwaves of goosebumps down your spine as she traces
    a sultry, perfectly-manicured finger along the spine of your complete Necronomicon
    and awaits your answer. You couldn't possibly give up your chance to date this
    stunning creature. Like, you literally can't stop trying.
  boon: If you fail a date roll against Beelzebabe, you can try to date them again.
  bane: Lose 3 Sanity
  boonBaneDialogue: 'Beelzebabe''s Blessing is that you get another chance. And no,
    you don''t have a choice. '
  dateOutcome: 'She thought she''d wring you dry, but wasn''t counting on a master
    of the Mystic and Dating Arts.  You''ve learned to see people (and demons) for
    who they really are, and you know all the best date spots in town.  You could
    work just to impress her, but you also see how hard it is to put up a front all
    the time.


    Your night on the town together is epic, but so is the relaxation
    afterwards.  You take her to the most relaxing spa in town, and finish in front
    of a cozy balefire wrapped in demon-fur robes while you mix up hot chocolate. 
    Sinfully dark and sweet, both.


    Maybe the real treasure was the experiences
    gained along the way, but a gorgeous demonic partner is also a pretty phenomenal
    result.'
  demonSprite: {fileID: 5912759927948260431, guid: d5e88fa6e12c4efd4896612dec4c8525, type: 3}
